column5: Thanks to everyone who makes this community the best fishing community on the web.... another milestone passed!!!  25 million page views!!!!  http://my.statcounter.com/project/standard...168&guest=1
If only you received 1$ per page load eh?
and we did it without Wayne around. posting..now that's hard to believe
Yeah, it's hard for him to make ends meet with only a penny a load.
Whats all the fuss about??????????????????????  Good on ya Boss.
I pretty much go on this forum everyday, probably like 10-15 times day lol
Congrats TJ, it is the best I have seen.

I am sure they are all coming to see me and find out my latest thoughts on life....... or not...... Congrates to the fearless leader and all of the owner/moderators for their selfless time and effort.   Art
That's great news TJ, thank you for providing the forum  Now everyone get back to work, tea time is over  John
I'm still viewing, I just don't have much time for posting.  I'm on vacation this week so I can post all I want.  Pam
love this site, hope it doesn't slow down during the cold monthes.
If they shut down the site, productivity in Ontario will shot up by at least a couple of percentage points.  LOL
Congrats TJ,Rick,Roy,Spiel,Dan,Muskiestud,Marty  and everyone who contributes in sharing their stories
I would be happy with even $0.01 per page
